channel.title: NewWorld - A Brand New Server Coming Your Way
channel.description:
[center][b]NewWorld - A Brand New Server Coming Your Way[/b][/center]
[i]Welcome. I'd just like to advertise this forum, please join it & contribute in any way you can.[/i]
[b][url=http://newworldserver.smfforfree3.com/index.php]NewWorld forum[/url][/b]
[i]May I ask that you also suggest anything that could help make this server better, in this thread. You do not need to join the forum, I will be reading this thread aswell as the forum to see what you've got to say.
Thank you.[/i]
[b]Edit[/b]
[i]This isn't a bribe. I'm merely telling you, the more you contribute & the more active you are, the higher your chances are of being a Moderator either on the server or the forum. If you want to be a Moderator, that is.[/i]
